  "3061330": {
    "name": "终极贪吃蛇",
    "steam_appid": 3061330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "欢迎踏入贪吃蛇的世界，这里汇聚了经典模式、丰富关卡、多样化游戏模式、个性化关卡定制以及缤纷色彩主题。<br><br>　　　　　　　　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/e5f7dfa4a9158c7badbb80c76204882d.webp?t=1724196881\" width=397 height=38 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >～ 经典模式 ～</h2>我们对手机上的贪吃蛇游戏进行了深入研究，经典模式将带您领略最原汁原味的贪吃蛇体验。移动、碰撞、按键反馈等细节均经过精心调校，力求还原原版贪吃蛇的精髓。此外，经典模式还设有全球排行榜，让您与亲朋好友一决高下。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/7f1fd9281b92036822ca5b0f52e83e0a.webp?t=1724196881\" width=205 height=56 /></span><br><br>　　　　　　　　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/e5f7dfa4a9158c7badbb80c76204882d.webp?t=1724196881\" width=397 height=38 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >~ 人机对战 ~</h2>在玩家与AI对战模式中，全新的挑战正等着您！您可以随时调节AI的强度，从简单到困难，随心所欲地选择您的对手。与电脑控制的智能蛇展开激烈对决，无论您是初学者还是高手，都能找到适合自己的挑战。展示您的技巧，征服AI对手，成为真正的贪吃蛇霸主！<br><br>　　　　　　　　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/22984b6bc20c0206f03f68450374a25d.avif?t=1724196881\" width=640 height=418 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >～ 娱乐模式 ～</h2>厌倦了传统的贪吃蛇玩法？想要尝试一些新奇的元素？娱乐模式将是您的不二之选！在这里，您可以让蛇吃到饱，穿墙而过，甚至施展其他特技，畅享贪吃蛇的无限可能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/441d6a427040661685a9ada168bc45bc.avif?t=1724196881\" width=172 height=140 /></span><br><br>　　　　　　　　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/e5f7dfa4a9158c7badbb80c76204882d.webp?t=1724196881\" width=397 height=38 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >～ 关卡模式 ～</h2>无论您喜欢循序渐进的挑战，还是喜欢在迷宫中探寻出路，关卡模式都能满足您的需求。数十个精心设计的关卡等待您的挑战，快来一展身手吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/d985380b2aea61b76921aad559c8510a.avif?t=1724196881\" width=422 height=276 /></span><br><br>　　　　　　　　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/e5f7dfa4a9158c7badbb80c76204882d.webp?t=1724196881\" width=397 height=38 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >～ 自定义关卡 ～</h2>如果您对现有关卡仍感不足，不妨尝试自定义关卡。只需一个文本编辑器，即可轻松创建属于您的独特关卡。蛇的长度、速度、地图边界、果子数量、障碍物摆放等要素均由您来决定，发挥创意，打造专属于您的关卡吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/2239a55bb3dd0b4620300d4e28d2df99.avif?t=1724196881\" width=296 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/d63b01ab7148354c9de7193aa8776937.avif?t=1724196881\" width=320 height=138 /></span><br><br>　　　　　　　　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/e5f7dfa4a9158c7badbb80c76204882d.webp?t=1724196881\" width=397 height=38 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >~ 回放 ~</h2>游戏的回放功能为玩家带来了一种全新的体验，让您能够重新审视并回顾自己的游戏过程。通过精确记录游戏中的每一个动作和决策，您可以在游戏结束后以旁观者的视角重温整个游戏历程。此外，回放功能还为玩家提供了一个分享和学习的平台，让您可以与朋友或家人分享自己的精彩瞬间，同时也能从其他玩家的回放中汲取灵感和经验，共同进步。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/7101a318ed0b894729460d390b5839fb.avif?t=1724196881\" width=448 height=336 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/06b275080b310a539b725841ebbd939e.avif?t=1724196881\" width=448 height=336 /></span><br><br>　　　　　　　　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/e5f7dfa4a9158c7badbb80c76204882d.webp?t=1724196881\" width=397 height=38 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >～ 颜色主题 ～</h2>游戏内置了多种颜色主题供您选择。若觉得这些还不够，您还可以通过修改配置文件来自定义更多颜色主题。界面中将展示您自定义的所有主题，方便您随时切换。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/ae4adc322966c4c34b4c5934482bb6ca.avif?t=1724196881\" width=322 height=148 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/73d8bc845cc91218e17524f693d55d76.avif?t=1724196881\" width=262 height=156 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/f6ecaadaff166b0ebffdd3025097c511.avif?t=1724196881\" width=348 height=114 /></span><br><br>　　　　　　　　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/e5f7dfa4a9158c7badbb80c76204882d.webp?t=1724196881\" width=397 height=38 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >～ 多语言 ～</h2>为了满足不同地区玩家的需求，游戏支持多语言。您不仅可以使用游戏自带的语言，还可以自行编写语言配置文件，让游戏更加贴近您的文化背景。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/71d301b8bcd6ece4d4ade2a200484e05.avif?t=1724196881\" width=320 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/015aaaff86db0bdf81ec692fb5724b17.avif?t=1724196881\" width=270 height=158 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/0e4ebf0dcf2adc68ecf5d66c0c91a858.avif?t=1724196881\" width=176 height=124 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061330/extras/2e49fb03f6bd5a6bfebbf054d6cd2fbd.avif?t=1724196881\" width=230 height=124 /></span>",
